Hands-on Practice

Open your browser and experiment with URLs.

Try changing:

- The path (`/login`, `/admin`, `/dashboard`)
- Query parameters (`?id=1`, `?page=2`)
- Fragments (`#about`, `#contact`)

Observe how each part changes the browser's behavior.

